Stephen D. Smith, NonFuel Minerals Statistical Summary, U.S. Geological Survey, Minerals Information, 1996, obtained from "http://minerals.er.usgs.gov/minerals/" on 11/4/98.
U.S. Geological Survey, "The Mineral Industry of [Illinois, Iowa, Minnesota, Missouri, and Wisconsin]," obtained from "http:// minerals.er.usgs.gov/minerals/" on 10/30/98.
